  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Since the absorption of clopidogrel through the gastrointestinal tract is limited, we want to
      examine whether adding clopidogrel by chewing will overcome the limited gastrointestinal
      absorption, and hence will improve the prevention of platelet aggregation.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
